i-font-family:"times="" roman""="">對</span><span lang="EN-US">1</span><span style="font-family:" 新細明體","serif";mso-ascii-font-family:="" "times="" new="" roman";mso-hansi-font-family:"times="" roman""="">商機媒合、成果展示以及產業交流等，希冀能夠透過表揚與卓越新創企業的經驗傳承，呈現臺灣新創企業傲人的創業成就。會中邀請到行政院張善政政務委員、國策顧問施顏祥顧問、工研院董事長蔡清彥、資策會執行長吳瑞北、英國貿易文化辦事處</span><span lang="EN-US">Sam Leng</span><span style="font-family:" 新細明體","serif";mso-ascii-font-family:="" "times="" new="" roman";mso-hansi-font-family:"times="" roman""="">處長及等產官學研超過</span><span lang="EN-US">500</span><span style="font-family:" 新細明體","serif";mso-ascii-font-family:="" "times="" new="" roman";mso-hansi-font-family:"times="" roman""="">人參加，共同見證優質育成企業加速成長茁壯成果。</span></p>', '2013/11/19', '', ''),
