span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:28.55pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:61.9pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-line-height-alt:0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">(一)<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">裡月多形設計目前所提供之產品已臻成熟，主要訴求點相當明確地針對了時下流行之中小型拍賣業者，所苦惱點貨、交貨之繁雜程式。透過該系統可無縫地與各式主流之網拍平臺結合，並能以<span lang="EN-US">GMAIL</span>統合管理訊息與電子郵件，真正減少賣家資訊不一致的窘境。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:28.55pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:61.9pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-line-height-alt:0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">(二)<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">而在軟硬整合的角度上，亦已結合實體倉儲業者，企盼扮演一關鍵仲介者，除了銜接賣家與倉儲業的橋樑，也透過此系統，做到提升自我價值之定位。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:28.55pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:61.9pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-line-height-alt:0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">(三)<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">惟此系統仍需強化的在於市場面上的行銷推廣，是否能有更積極的訂價策略，以吸引更多網拍賣家的青睞，進而採用；此外，<span lang="EN-US">must be </span>以及<span lang="EN-US"> nice to have</span>的思維定論，也就是沒有了此系統，網拍賣家覺得如何<span lang="EN-US">? </span>這決定了系統的獨特性以及占有力道；在推廣面上，因應華文電子商務的興盛，中國平臺業者的節節進逼，相對於服務提供者反而是個機會，如何與之介接，也考驗著服務業者的競爭力與洞悉力；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:28.55pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:61.9pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-line-height-alt:0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">(四)<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">最後，踩在巨人的肩膀上，是裡月多形最好的佈署心法，也就是依靠大廠平臺，如上架至<span lang="EN-US">Google Apps</span>，讓更多業者看到該產品，重點不只在於當下此產品，而應是著眼于未來搭上此波電子商務的復蘇力道，做為一關鍵的流程、功能整合者，才能彰顯自我特色。<strong><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:28.55pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:37.9pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-line-height-alt:0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:標楷體;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold">二、<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold">財務</span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體">管理<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:28.55pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:61.9pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-line-height-alt:0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">(一)<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">財務管理對於中小企業一直以來總是被視為是次要選項，並非為財務不重要，只是在技術為發展主力階段的公司而言，花錢總是無法手軟。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:28.55pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:61.9pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-line-height-alt:0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo4"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:標楷體;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold">(二)<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">而裡月多形設計成立至今已屆<span lang="EN-US">8</span>年，在自有產品終於成熟接軌市場後，再下來即是必須思考財務面上的的調控，也就是一套較為合理的財務規劃，去明訂人事、研發、設備、行銷等成本的開支比例，以求得更好的公司營運狀況。在此仍將建議，除了與既有的會計師配合，亦將引薦目前像是中小企業處的財管輔導計畫的協助，其他像是地方政府，如新北市亦有提供的財會輔導措施，都是很好的立即資源可供運用。</span><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:28.55pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:37.9pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-line-height-alt:0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:標楷體;\r\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold">三、<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold">研發</span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體">貸款<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:28.55pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:37.9pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:0pt"><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">在此研發貸款上，除了持續關注政府研發補助資源，像是現在開跑的<span lang="EN-US">102</span>年<span lang="EN-US">SIIR</span>服務業研發補助計畫，就相當適合裡月多形設計申請。其他也包含相關人力訓練之補貼等。假以時日，裡月多形亦可注意中小企業處的創新研究獎項，以獨特之研發產品來競逐。</span><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:95.05pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:6.8gd;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-13.45pt;mso-char-indent-count:-.96;\r\nline-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly"><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:13.9pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:13.9pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-13.9pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly;layout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><strong><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt">陸、臨時動議</span></strong><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:標楷體;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="2" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;mso-para-margin-bottom:\r\n.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly"><span style="font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-fon