an><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">各種評量工具、方式，包括職能問卷、評鑒中心、<span lang="EN-US">360 </span>度回饋、標竿法等。</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體; color: #222222; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">客戶並包含本會之數教所。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:36.0pt;mso-para-margin-left:1.0gd;\r\ntext-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">二、<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">而今將</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">聚焦於<span lang="EN-US">ICT</span>的體現，使之成為新一代人才評量機制的良好工具，因此希望申請今年度的<span lang="EN-US">SIIR</span>計畫，同時以<span lang="EN-US">B2B</span>角度，亦即大企業內<span lang="EN-US">HR</span>整合為行銷重點，重點因此將聚焦於產品領域的定位。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:36.0pt;mso-para-margin-left:1.0gd;\r\ntext-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">三、<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">在過程中，主要厘清產品進度，也包含陳述中要分別說明機制面、技術面以及行銷面，藉以強化心理學理論的有理有據，同時在技術面也強調目前既有的基礎不是憑空而來，是有這麼長久的發展而下，之後再以多個成功的客戶夥伴的合作，帶出行銷面未來的前景看好。未來</span><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體; color: #222222; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">並將考慮以園區企業為協助推廣試驗點。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:36.0pt;mso-para-margin-left:1.0gd;\r\ntext-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">四、<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">針對簡報審查，仍以基本邏輯出發，由背景動機，營運模式、定價策略、行銷模式、品質化指標、甘特圖<span lang="EN-US">+</span>查核點、財務規劃，當然仍要強調為何是你能做<span lang="EN-US">? </span>贏過競爭對手的地方，以及市場如何介接。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:3.0pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly"><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:標楷體">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:13.9pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:13.9pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-13.9pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly;layout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><strong><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt">陸、臨時動議</span></strong><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:標楷體;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="2" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;mso-para-margin-bottom:\r\n.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly"><span style="font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font