nbsp;</span></p>\r\n </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:13.9pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:13.9pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-13.9pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly;layout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><strong><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt">伍、討論事項及裁示：</span></strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:標楷體;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:51.25pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:51.25pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US">一、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family:\r\n標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">因應中心思考強化輔導強度，企盼逐步建立各小主題型企業群聚，以拉動進駐企業彼此之間異業合作、互利共生機會，真正創造實質成長，育成中心除了塑造整體框架方向與環境，並引入政令工具資源以及臨時需求滿足，建立育成中心輔導角色之高度。並邀請大型企業涉入擔任業師引導。，而後建立完整專業後勤，包含財管、經營、法律、智財、技術、行銷等，以支援各式小型群聚體發展。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:51.25pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:51.25pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US">二、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family:\r\n標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">三艾健康已有明確健康雲之發展模式與產品，執行長背景為工研院相關政府健康照護計畫之擘畫者，此次創業除繼續發展完善</span><span lang="EN-US">B2B2C</span><span style="font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">之雲端平臺、以及</span><span lang="EN-US">KIOSK</span><span style="font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">照護站，更企盼深化行動端應用。而嵐奕科技一直以來即擅長於手機行動專案開發，目前亦恰好有慕尼克保險專案之開發，對於用戶健康評估之機制亦有涉獵。兩者預定下周邀請相關醫師專家共同與會洽談深度合作。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:51.25pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:51.25pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US">三、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family:\r\n標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">針對上述合作，個人還將引薦外部企業</span><span lang="EN-US">_</span><span style="font-family:\r\n標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">中邦資訊投入行動端用藥辨識之環節，加強營運模式之廣度；以及元智大學資管系謝瑞建教授投入行動心電圖功能，並可擔任業師角色，除了能考慮以產學合作之作法，亦能將上述包裝成健康雲之小研發聯盟，強化整體運作。而叡揚資訊將能參與雲端產品之經驗賦予以及行銷面合作。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:13.9pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:13.9pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-13.9pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-heig