le:\r\nexactly;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US">二、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family:\r\n標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">胡修武副主任主要表示，資策會在南京的確著墨甚深，特別是今日落地于麒麟兩岸中小企業台商科創園，並承接展示中心之業務，深刻結合計畫群聚之概念，希望塑造出臺商第一線前進基地之態勢，並求聚合資源、人脈、行銷、平臺等作法，真正達到協助台商落地以及媒合各方資源之整合模式。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:51.25pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:51.25pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US">三、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family:\r\n標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">胡副主任其次表示，相當歡迎臉書雲端至麒麟實地評估。目前麒麟科創園在交通上仍持續建設，預計</span><span lang="EN-US">2014</span><span style="font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">即有</span><span lang="EN-US">2</span><span style="font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">號地鐵線于馬群站上線，相當便捷；而住屋上，按需求</span><span lang="EN-US">100</span><span style="font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">平方米，也能協調提供獨立空間滿足；人力招募上，也可協調當地人員協助</span><span lang="EN-US">”</span><span style="font-family:標楷體;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">前程無憂</span><span lang="EN-US">”</span><span style="font-family:\r\n標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">等平臺資源，最後公司成立是陸資還是外資，則仍需相當評估。</span><span lang="EN-US"><