style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:\r\nwidow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 標楷體;">一、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: 標楷體;">戲智科技自過往的<span lang="EN-US">APP</span>行動遊戲開發，轉型至自有平板電腦之生產，訴求在於軟硬整合思維下之差異化利基，拉大與市場對手差距，在未來並將持續透過專屬客制行銷案<span lang="EN-US">(W hotel</span>的隨身客房平板服務系統、華納兄弟之新超人電影主題平板<span lang="EN-US">)</span>，一點一點地強化戲智科技之品牌與成案競爭力，為戲智科技打下深耕臺灣，佈局全球之基礎。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:\r\nwidow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 標楷體;">二、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: 標楷體;">育成中心 洪副處長表示除了整合資金、人脈等資源，更將協助於行銷通路的搭建與媒合，特別是<span lang="EN-US">POC</span>創案，同時積極引入相關異業合作機會與產業聯盟引薦，希望能夠讓戲智科技持續提高能見度，並以優異的研發能量和產品部署，逐步站穩市場。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:\r\nwidow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 標楷體;">三、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: 標楷體;">育成中心亦企盼後續針對<span lang="EN-US">B2B</span>之特定領域、產業<span lang="EN-US">APP</span>來合作，借重戲智科技長年來在<span lang="EN-US">APP</span>的深耕經驗，與數位內容產業推動辦公室有更緊密之連結，並且透過主動廣宣，和引薦相關國內外投資案等，形塑更具實質效益之商機促成。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:\r\nwidow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 標楷體;">四、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: 標楷體;">在財務面部分，戲智科技徐董事長亦表示在今年<span lang="EN-US">10</span>月前，資金周轉的確較為辛苦，但極具誠意希望和育成中心互相協調，至少在延遲繳款此一面向上，除了先繳清舊有欠款，也會留意未來的繳款時間。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:\r\nwidow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 標楷體;">五、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: 標楷體;">戲智科技在今年開始，與資誠積極配合進行<span lang="EN-US">IPO</span>準備，同時亦因第三代平板電腦開發完成，於<span lang="EN-US">6</span>月初<span lang="EN-US">COMPUTEX</span>展順利展出，<span lang="EN-US">10</span>月份更將參加日本<span lang="EN-US">IT PRO</span>展。育成中心亦將依循政府長官的期許，協助引入更多政府相關資源以及像是數位內容產業推動辦公室資源等，真正為戲智科技之成長盡一份心力。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:3.0pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><strong><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:93.15pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:6.8gd;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-11.55pt;mso-char-indent-count:-.96"><strong><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:13.9pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:13.9pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-13.9pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly;layout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><strong><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt">陸、臨時動議</span></strong><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:標楷體;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="2" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;mso-para-margin-bottom:\r\n.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:0cm;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:ex