ra-margin-left:13.9pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-13.9pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly;layout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><strong><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt">伍、討論事項及裁示：</span></strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:標楷體;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 24pt; text-indent: -24pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:\r\n標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:標楷體;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:0pt">一、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family:\r\n標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:0pt">有鑒於希望與園區建立更緊密關係，同時有利於中心進駐企業的產品廣宣，因此與園區服務中心論及潛在合作機會。首先是針對<span lang="EN-US">DEMO SITE</span>建立，以園區<span lang="EN-US">2</span>樓<span lang="EN-US">-</span>雲端智慧展示館為展示區，引入更多雲端產品<span lang="EN-US">/</span>服務內容，除充實展示能量，也能使該區成為外賓參訪重點。後續導入收費機制以及維運細節必須再討論。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#222222;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 24pt; text-indent: -24pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:標楷體;color:#222222;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt">二、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt">其次，是關於中心商品展售櫃之想法，服務中心也恰好想要建立禮贈品中心，開發園區相關紀念品以及設計商品，藉此展現園區特色。本中心亦可藉此引入文創產業之實體商品上架販賣，以及相關經營。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoListParagraph"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:0pt">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 24pt; text-indent: -24pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:標楷體;color:#222222;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt">三、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt">最後，在<span lang="EN-US">Coworking space</span>的部分，陳主任也建議可參考學學文創之場地經營作法，例如比照學學文創扶植新銳設計師做法，辦公室就是在育成中心，設計商品就在禮贈品中心販賣，如此強化引入誘因。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:3.0pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:標楷體">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:51.25pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:51.25pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:13.9pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:13.9pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-13.9pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly;layout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><strong><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt">陸、臨時動議</span></strong><