30.3pt;line-height:\r\n20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">二、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">針對于阿碼繼續延駐，基本上中企處是同意，但需要請阿碼科技對於南港軟體育成中心有所回饋機制。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:48.3pt;text-indent:-30.3pt;line-height:\r\n20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">三、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">阿碼科技黃耀文執行長提出以下可以回饋的作法：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:60.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:\r\n20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 60.0pt"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">1.<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">租金不同：<span lang="EN-US"><br>\r\n</span>阿碼科技在延駐期間租金增加<span lang="EN-US">20%</span>，已與新進駐廠商有所不同。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:60.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:\r\n20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 60.0pt"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">2.<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">經驗分享及傳承：<span lang="EN-US"><br>\r\n</span>許多新創廠商對於如何取得資金、面對創投等經驗不足，阿碼科技對於這方面的經驗相當豐富，可以用來教導育成中心內的新創廠商，並可以安排活動與進駐廠商交流或是固定時間的研討會等。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:60.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:\r\n20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 60.0pt"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">3.<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">建立上下游的關係：<span lang="EN-US"><br>\r\n</span>阿碼科技願意以大帶小，建立業務合作關係。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:60.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:\r\n20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 60.0pt"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">4.<span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">以量化資料展現亮點：<span lang="EN-US"><br>\r\n</span>針對於就業數、國際業務合作、營收、國際專利數、國際獎項、國內外媒體報導數量，都可以提供每年應達成之指標。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:48.3pt;text-indent:-30.3pt;line-height:\r\n20.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">四、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 標楷體;">針對阿碼所提出的相關回饋，將在近期內在與中企處討論後，決定延駐相關回饋之訂定。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.5pt;\r\nmargin-left:93.15pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:6.8gd;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-11.55pt;mso-char-indent-count:-.96"><strong><span 