soNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:51.25pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:51.25pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US">二、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family:\r\n標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">普羅斯主要由嵌入式系統廠出發，掌握一些晶片設計技術以及開案能力，目前主要進軍無線音訊應用。除了在今年開始研發完成設計雛形，也開始參展加強曝光。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:51.25pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:51.25pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US">三、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family:\r\n標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">無論是否需要作價，但對於公司本身而言，自有技術保護仍是關鍵議題，因此訴諸於專利保護即是現下許多公司的做法。目前所需在意的還是此專利是否由公司成員開發之資產，還是先由個人外部帶進來，視為技術入股，而此均影響未來公司對於股權分配的規劃。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:51.25pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;mso-para-margin-right:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.25gd;mso-para-margin-left:51.25pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\r\nexactly;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US">四、</span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family:\r\n標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">因應目前手邊所有</span